  "description": [
    "REAL ESTATE CASE ORDER DENYING BECEIV\u00cfLt XN KENYONCANNON SUIT RICH PROPERTY IS CONCERNED Evidence Shows That Parties to Action Own Seven Hundred Lots and Twelve Thousand Dollars in Good Accounts The longdrawn out hearing In the real esttate case In Judge Clancys court In which D E Kenyon sued John O Cannon and others for an accounting came to an end yesterday evening and Judge Clancy refused to grant Kenyons prayer for a receiver to take charge of the property at issue Kenyon and Cannon are joint owners In 700 lots in the South Park addition of Butte and were conducting a real estate business in the sale of the lots Cannon was trustee for the property He denied Kenyon access to the books of accounts and Kenyon brought the suit The order denying the receivership was a victory on its face for the defendants but the suit for an accounting Is still pending and the evidence given at the hearing Just over revealed to Kenyon the condition of the property and what Its value is at present His Interest is a third and he calims to have put 6000 In the business The testimony showed that there are 700"
  ],
